Template: ispconfig-zabbix-monitoring/ispconfig_url
Type: string
Default: https://localhost:8080/remote/
Description: ISPConfig Remote API URL
 Enter the URL of your ISPConfig Remote API endpoint including protocol and port.
 .
 Example: https://panel.example.com:8080/remote/

Template: ispconfig-zabbix-monitoring/ispconfig_username
Type: string
Default: remote_user
Description: ISPConfig Remote API username
 Enter the username for ISPConfig Remote API access.
 This user should have appropriate permissions for monitoring.

Template: ispconfig-zabbix-monitoring/ispconfig_password
Type: password
Description: ISPConfig Remote API password
 Enter the password for the ISPConfig Remote API user.
 .
 This password will be stored in /etc/ispconfig-zabbix-monitoring/config.php
 with restricted permissions (readable only by root and zabbix).
